    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Grids of fine opaque lines or other fine opaque patterns through which images are photographed to break up tonal areas into fine patterns for creating tonal areas in printing.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
